             <Markdown>
                 ## Priorities for Successful Writing
                 
                 In the screens that follow, you will explore which goals you think are important
                 for writing success. Each screen will present four goals that writer might adopt
                 at some point in the writing process. Decide which are more important and which
                 are less important, and indicate your decisions by dragging and dropping the
                 statements into priority order, where (1) is the highest priority and (4) is the lowest priority.
             </Markdown>
    </Vertical>
