            to least important (bottom):
        </Markdown>
        <SortableInput id="wpj2_sortable1" dragMode="whole">
            <TextBlock>Using sophisticated words and well-developed sentences.</TextBlock>
            <TextBlock>Figuring out what one really thinks about a topic before writing.</TextBlock>
            <TextBlock>Taking the time to understand assignments before starting to write.</TextBlock>            
            <TextBlock>Expressing ideas accurately.</TextBlock>
        </SortableInput>
    </Vertical>
